Image Prompt:
Generate an image showing a serene and peaceful landscape with a clear blue sky, fluffy white clouds, and rays of sunlight breaking through. In the center of the image, depict a gentle dove flying gracefully, symbolizing the presence and care of God. Surround the dove with subtle hints of nature such as blooming flowers and lush greenery to convey a sense of divine love and protection. This image should evoke feelings of comfort, hope, and the idea that God's care is ever-present in the world.
